Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:46.64,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 25 - When I'm Out of Luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this problem is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,23 minus 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to solve something that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can subtract 5 from 8, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,5 from 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy. It'd be 2, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,8, subtract 5 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:23.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be doing calculations in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you can subtract 5 from 8,\Nyou should be able to solve that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can I, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:38.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,6, 7, 8, 9, 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,11, 12...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the problem for Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Divide 125 by 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Division is my forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:48.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,15, 16, 17, 18, 19, 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,20. 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, I need you to lend me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need 23 fingers to solve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:00.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:01.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of counting with fingers,\Ndo it in your mind! In the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you're noisy! Can't you scratch less? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May! What's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hate arithmetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:20.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you say you hate it,\Ndoes that mean you won't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:25.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Um, I mean, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:29.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you're fine with growing up\Ninto an adult who can't even do basic reckoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:30.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Put your mind to it, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I really only have 20 fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's no disaster, Lucy.\NLet me teach you just the way to do it:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:42.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,First, you subtract 17\Nfrom your 20 fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:44.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Subtract 17 from 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:46.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And then you just add 3 to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! If I do that, my 20 fingers would suffice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:53.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Enough giving unwanted\Ninstructions to neighbors! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:56.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, if the total of fingers I have is 20...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:59.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, why don't you work on the division\Nof 125 by 5 which equals 25...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, you got that right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:01.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I subtract 17 from it, it's 1, 2, 3, 4, 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Told you, this problem is too much a cakewalk, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,6, 7, 8, 9, 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, that's insolent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't I give you a better problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:09.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,11, 12, 13, 14, 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's try this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,16, 17...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:14.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,2279 divided by 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's suddenly too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And now, what remains is... What remains is 1, 2, 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,2279 isn't divisible by 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,3 fingers, then. 3, that means... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're so noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:28.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To be divisible by 5, the number\Nneeds to end with 5 or 0, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yes, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:34.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... And how much was I supposed to add to my 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why did I give you a problem like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:36.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess math isn't your own forte, is it, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How much did she say before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, talking back to teacher like that is insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh why do I have such loud sisters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Studying inside. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:11.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, every Saturday afternoon\Nthey're having classes in the house, and it's set.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I feel rightly sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When it's rainin' hard,\Nclasses are more or less tolerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But not when the weather's that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? So your studying is governed by weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:28.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure Kate's gonna study all day long today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:32.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If they do it all day, I bet Lucy would drop dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure am sorry for those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:39.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm done with this work,\NI'd probably go help out Kate and Lucy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:44.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel like lending me a bit of a hand\Nwith my work until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging out with Ben is aight, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where you're gonna live?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Both me and Dr. Deighton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:06:00.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As for the roof, we'll have no choice\Nbut to have your dad make it for us. That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come to an answer like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:10.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:14.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we subtract 9 from 90, right? So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It'd be 81!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, how can you be that inattentive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You could've solved it if you really tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're in a hurry, you can't get anything done. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't immerse in anything. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:26.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Immerse? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy with doing arithmetic now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:32.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At such times, you should focus\Nall of your attention on arithmetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:35.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When there are no other things on your mind,\Nthat's called immersion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Then it's hopeless for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:42.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm thinking about the goat milk\NI'm supposed to give to Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:54.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've not been studying like this\Nfor a long time, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've completely forgotten\Nour scholarly habits. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, Lucy's inability to focus\Nis probably because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This time, calm down before starting, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look at those two racking their brains\Nas best they can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually done since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Billy came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine - he brought his goat along\Nall the way from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Will be there right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not you! Not before you solve this problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead now, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll finish in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you finished your work, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:38.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When dad returns, tell him I went fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:38.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Finished so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:58.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How come 199 minus 109 is 9?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:05.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we take 199 and subtract 109, right? Thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,100 minus 100 is zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then we subtract 9 from 99...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's 90!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How inattentive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A pups! Aintcha a cute one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just a dog, but a dingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Bollocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a baby dingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:28.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you're not messing with me, aintcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:32.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A dingo is supposed to have a habit\Nof eating sheep and other livestock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's him.\NAnd his name is Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you'd better not wake him. There's no telling\Nwhich one of you would be more scared. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? So a dingo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, he turned out to be surprisingly smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:53.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you really a dingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He really is! Staring so intently at my goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he just liked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:07.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's used to attacking sheep.\NSo he'd gladly take a bite from a goat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He only likes goats for playing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme show you quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure it's aight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:28.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! If we also let that goat in,\Nthat'd be like a long-awaited family reunion! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:28.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:31.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Those three are almost like siblings-in-law by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:42.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little had only grown that big\Nthanks to Sticky's milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:52.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's almost unbelievable\Nhe'd grow to become a dingo one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:58.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here you go.\NWe're finally home, Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Thanks a lot, you're a saver!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Ben had finished working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a little rough on the edges. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like Ben's work at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:24.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like lately\Nhe's not been very earnest about his work. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:36.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Mac finally showed up outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she just watering her flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to know she recovered enough\Nto leave her house again. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:47.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's been a month\Nsince her husband passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:51.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But it still pains her a great deal, I imagine. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:51.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Muster your courage and do another one. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Without that, you won't get any playtime today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying my best,\Nbut I can't get her to study seriously. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see Billy came to visit us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:12.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm telling her to calm down.\NOtherwise, she'll never learn to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as she's distracted, she makes a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:16.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I think you should call it a day, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate is already playing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By saying so, you're letting her\Nabuse your kindness in the future, father! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Lucy-May. From the next time on,\Nyou'll put every effort into studying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:28.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not convinced! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious about doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Go play outside, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, father, you're hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If she was slacking off up until now,\Nonly radical measures would've worked!  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where exactly did Ben go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You look properly squeezed up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Billy! G'day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye. Good job, I guess. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Took your sweet time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause I solved ten more problems since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally enough, all of them perfectly! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the time dad returned there,\NI was already allowed to go play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Though I would gladly keep cracking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:19.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's mighty odd of our fella Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He goes fishing, but brings along a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That book is a Latin grammar textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Does he hope to increase his fishing luck\Nthrough reading that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our brother is one peculiar fella in general!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:35.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He said he likes to study, can you imagine that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where would we go to play now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What should we play?\NHave you decided already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, you've become so heavy, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:17.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave my goat in here,\Nit'll be alright, wouldn't it, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:22.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like they still remember they're a family! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Mrs. Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while since I last visited you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! And that must be the baby dingo, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Did Mr. Bernard tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:40.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It may be docile for now, but even a baby dingo\Nis still a dingo, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep a close eye on him at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, that parcel smells awfully good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, just some buns. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:53.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've not baked any in ages.\NMake sure to try it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:54.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Set out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:18.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Faster now! Faster, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we catch a wild hare today, what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:27.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it, of course! No two ways about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:40.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I was also considering returning to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I'd have returned,\NI no longer had any close relatives there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:47.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And since even my brother moved here,\NI made up my mind on staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:53.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you god dragged to here after Mr. Bernard,\Nyour reliable little brother? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:55.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about the reliable part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:15:00.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Henceforth and forever, please feel free to tell us\Nwhenever there's anything we could help you with. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:05.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About that... Actually, I came here to ask for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:08.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Ms. Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How can Clara help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I have long planned\Nto start a business, you see. And for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:18.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping Ms. Clara would be so kind\Nas to assist me with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of business?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:23.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A bakery. If there's something\NI know how to do, it's baking. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My brother had also approved the idea.\NHe was all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:33.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll delight everyone greatly\Nif you become a professional bread-maker. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:39.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, I would be happy to help\Nin any way I can with your shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:45.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With that settled, I will start\Nlooking for a shop as soon as tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This place is where Colonel Light ran into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did Colonel say that the local scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:58.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,reminds him of that in the English village\Nof Theberton, where he lived as a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:03.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel's health has deteriorated in recent years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:07.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\Nhe was coughing quite a lot while we spoke. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,His chest is giving him trouble, it seems. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But because he's the most important man around,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:15.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,when Surveyor-General's health is failing,\Nnobody can get anything done. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:20.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, my father also\Nstill can't get the land promised to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:24.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing that is what actually stings me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:27.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone rushed to this country,\Nallured by its spacious lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:31.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in fact, we're now sitting on the piles of land\Nyet to be surveyed, that we can't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:36.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The folk that come here in droves\Nall find themselves in the same situation as your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:37.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's just too unfair. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:41.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. And still, as you said,\Nnobody can get anything done. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Surveying the wilderness is no cakewalk, Ben. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:50.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also considering resigning from office work,\Nso that I could go conduct actual surveying on-site.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:56.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if you'll be constantly away on expeditions,\Nwouldn't your sister get lonely? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Leave my sister to me, I'll think of something. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she's got grit in her. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:03.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I've been wondering\Nabout that thing for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean this?\NIt's a textbook on Latin grammar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Troi... Toroi... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a single chance to use Latin\Never since I graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:23.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Every night, Dr. Deighton\Nteaches me some of it, one bit at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you can rely on that wacky doctor? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he even knows what he is teaching you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you don't trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:35.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! You should know that doctor\Nis a terrible alcoholic. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not trust him much with anything.\NLatin included. Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no one else to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Mr. Bernard, perhaps, if you know Latin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless. Hopeless! Totally hopeless. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:57.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This looks a lot\Nlike a heavy rain about to start, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Found it, found it!\NIt's here! Here, Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It went that way! Catch it now, Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, it's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don't get in the way, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:16.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That bunch sure can afford being carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! It's right there! Right there, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Why couldn't you do just a bit more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:52.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a shame, you were really close this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look like it'll stop soon... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. Let's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Comment: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The rabbit from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking shelter under the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, that's just so provocative! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's our brother right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone stay low, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While Ben is so absentminded,\NI'll go scare him to death! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:46.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The book!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A success! You should've seen your face, brother! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:52.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped my Latin grammar textbook in the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What am I to do now?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:07.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:10.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bother, please
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:29.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Keeps crying and says she won't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:48.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:56.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Ben.\NAren't you going to forgive Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:57.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:03.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, Lucy never wanted\Nfor the book to fall in the river when doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:08.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help noticing that you work\Nsomewhat half-heartedly these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As shown by the brickwork as well. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That grammar textbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something you really need that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:20.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to say that you'll need Latin to be a farmer? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That was a very important book,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:28.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,that village pastor Kramer gave me, instructing me to study it when I get to Australia. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:34.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But let me put this straight for you -\Nyou don't need that book right now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:37.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just focusing on the work\Ndirectly before us is more than enough. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:39.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:43.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not eating! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:26.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I'll probably have a chance\Nto buy a new book later, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:34.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:40.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will try apologizing once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:46.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He may be right that I don't really\Nneed that book right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:50.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll become of the essence in the future!\NRight, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:05.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, Little is feeling completely neglected, Lucy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:15.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:20.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really, really never wanted you\Nto drop that book when doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:21.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:23.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will you forgive me, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:24.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:30.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, how about we go have our supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.40,0:23:38.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That day, Lucy was well and truly out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:39.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:43.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:47.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's nothing. I'm f—Ouch! 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:51.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There are days like that, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:58.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the incident with brother's Latin grammar textbook turned out to be a particularly nasty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,During the night, I suddenly develop a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:11.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In more pain than I can take, I keep muttering through delirium, "I'm sorry" and "Forgive me".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.32,0:24:14.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"I Fell Ill!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.98,0:24:16.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
